:{{DIcon|Talk}} Tell me about the Divination Commission...
::<!--Trigger PerformanceE 502031103: Config/Level/NPCDialogue/P10202/F10202001_G43/Act/Act_502031103.json-->
::'''Huixing:''' Alright. I'll try to keep things brief, as we do lots of different things here.
::<!--Custom String Trigger: Wait_Option_502031101_22-->
::<!--Custom String Listener: Wait_Option_502031101_22-->
::{{DIcon|Talk}} What does the Divination Commission do?
:::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_502031111-->
:::'''Huixing:''' Calculations.
:::'''Huixing:''' ...
:::'''Huixing:''' ...My response has left you dissatisfied.
:::'''Huixing:''' We calculate the Luofu's trajectory as it sails and help it avoid any dangerous routes. When moored, we calculate and track the movements of the celestial bodies around us.
:::'''Huixing:''' Changes in star temperature, fluctuations in gravity waves... The delves seemingly isolate us from the rest of the universe, but our fates are still impacted by the expanse.
:::'''Huixing:''' The Divination Commission's most important day-to-day work is observing these changing phenomena, gathering information, calculating the probabilities of certain occurrences, and proposing contingencies.
:::'''Huixing:''' Has the answer sated your curiosity?
::;(Return to previous option selection (cloneCheckString))
::{{DIcon|Talk}} Is it true that the Matrix of Prescience can predict the future?
:::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_502031119-->
:::'''Huixing:''' Affirmative.
:::'''Huixing:''' ...
:::'''Huixing:''' ...I guess you'd like to know more details? Sorry, the technical details are all confidential. All I can say is a story to sate your curiosity.
:::'''Huixing:''' Xianzhou had once visited a world where the residents used something called an Aquascope to scry into the future. That thing was even more accurate than the Matrix of Prescience, and our exploration team couldn't help but pore ourselves into researching this technology.
:::'''Huixing:''' We later came to realize that this Aquascope was no mystery at all. That world simply has a limited amount of information. There wasn't much computational power and data input needed to predict the future there.
:::'''Huixing:''' In comparison, the Luofu sails through galaxies of stars, not a machine-esque world as predictable as a complex clockwork of unerring precision.
:::'''Huixing:''' And so... Can the Matrix of Prescience divine the future? Yes. Is it accurate? Based on the voluminous calculations run daily by the Divination Commission: Not accurate enough.
:::'''Huixing:''' Perhaps I strayed off-topic a bit there, but that's really all I can say.
::;(Return to previous option selection (cloneCheckString))
::{{DIcon|Exit}} I have nothing else to ask.
:::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_502031129-->
:::'''Huixing:''' Alright. So long.
:::<!--Ends the current performance-->
