::'''Huixing:''' Jingzhai, our Managing Diviner? Why do you ask?
::'''Huixing:''' As usual, Jingzhai is dedicated to her work and very organized. I think she's doing quite well.
::'''Huixing:''' Things at the Divination Commission have been hectic lately, and we often have to work overtime. Jingzhai always does the extra work without complaining. She has a great personality and excels at what she does. She is an amazing colleague.
::<!--Ends the current performance-->
